    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a true collector-grade example, meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior finish is breathtaking, showcasing a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, all protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather bolsters show no signs of entry wear, the carpets are spotless, and every electronic feature functions with factory precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach\u2014every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, and I have a complete binder of maintenance records to verify its history. It drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot: tight, responsive, and whisper-quiet. This vehicle has never seen rain, has no modifications, and carries a clean title. I welcome and encourage any third-party inspection to verify that this car is as close to new as possible.",
